Apakah karena
Sai di rumah sakit?

00:15:44.699 --> 00:15:46.490
Tolong jangan berdebat sekarang.

00:15:46.532 --> 00:15:47.823
Sunny, biarkan dia masuk.

00:15:47.906 --> 00:15:49.490
Pulkit ada.
Dia akan merawatnya.

00:15:49.574 --> 00:15:50.532
Ayo cepat.

